# AGENTS.md — {{projectName}}

Guide for AI coding assistants working on this Python project.

## Commands

| Task | Command |
|------|---------|
| Everything | `make qa` |
| Tests | `pytest --cov --cov-report=term-missing` |
| Lint | `ruff check src/` |
| Type-check | `mypy src/` |

## Conventions

- **Type annotations required** on all public functions (mypy strict).
- **CLI tests** use `click.testing.CliRunner` (see `tests/test_main.py`).
- **Logging** goes to stderr via `logging.StreamHandler`; CLI output goes to stdout via `click.echo`.
- **No network calls in unit tests** — mock external HTTP with `responses` or `pytest-httpx`.
